cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.SI. 

The paper proposes a novel method for next location prediction using travel time information, which involves machine learning and data analysis techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper deals with large datasets and proposes a new model, which suggests that it could also fit into cs.DB (Databases) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-categories.
